earn_dialog_desc:
Welcome to "Wisal" App!

We offer you a chance to collect points and win amazing rewards on the "Wisal" app! How?

1. Total Points:

Every time you do something in the app like reading news, watching ads, or even playing games, you earn points.
2. Total Earned Balance:

Save those points and use them to get rewards and benefit from our cool offers.
3. App Prizes:

Every day, you'll find new and exclusive prizes in the "Prizes" section. Go in and win!
4. Login Prizes:

Just log into the app daily and get prizes. Every day, you'll have a new reward waiting for you.
5. Referral System:

Share the app with your friends, and when they sign up through you, you'll get rewards for each one who signs up.
6. Free Points Opportunities:

You can easily earn points by watching our ads, videos, or even filling out our surveys.
That's it! And remember, you can convert all these points into real money on Vodafone Cash or any other wallet!
